  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to assess the effect of a low-glycemic-load and milk-free diet
      on acne severity.

      IGF-1 and a phosphorylated product of the mTORC pathway (p70S6K) will be assessed in both
      groups to explore the mTORC signaling pathway, which is thought to be related to clinical
      improvement in previous studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
